title: Hour 3 - Matt Rhule Fired, Cooper Rush Steady
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Matt Rhule Fired, Cooper Rush Steady
description:
Dan wasn't surprised to hear that the Carolina Panthers fired head coach Matt Rhule. And he thinks Cooper Rush is effective with the Dallas Cowboys because he knows his limitations.
